{
  "stem": "11998.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could smell the burning-- burning flesh, or-- you know, it was-- it was definitely a stink.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And depending on the wind, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The wind blew our way, we could smell it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If the wind blew the other way, we didn't smell it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We found out that some people-- they came into the camp and asked for volunteers to go and do some jobs outside to-- and the people who were volunteered came back, and they said that they were working alongside the women.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father decided that he would like to [DRINKS WATER] go and see if he could contact my mother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because as my mother saw me, she saw me in the-- in the lineup with the young men-- young boys and old men.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she thought that I was-- went to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By that time she, you know, already knew what was happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- do you want to shut the furnace off?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At any rate-- the-- so he found out that the women-- that the men saw the women.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he wanted-- so he-- he volunteered to go to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He volunteered to go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he left early in the morning, must have been, maybe, 8 o'clock, 7 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he came-- usually, they came back about 5 or 6 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this time, they didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was-- by that time, it was already September.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the days were getting shorter.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was getting dark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I could see the flames against the sky, shooting out of the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'm thinking that my father must be among those flames.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My father's soul must be going up.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
